JASMIN Analysis Platform : Vagrant VM configuration
===================================================

This repository will create a VM with the JASMIN Analysis Platform installed.  It requires VirtaulBox and Vagrant.

As currently written it will only work within the RAL network.

Getting Started
---------------

 1. Install VirtualBox
 2. Install Vagrant
 3. Run "vagrant up"
 4. visit the VM with "vagrant ssh"

